  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0baf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Mayantha Dissanayake did not leave the party - United People's Shakti",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The party has declared that the reports that Member of Parliament Mayanta Dissanayake has left United People's Shakti are untrue.",
        "It is reported that he has only resigned from the position of the youth organization of United People's Shakti, which he held till now.",
        "Rehan Jayawickrama, Vice President of United People's Shakti's Youth Organization, said in his Twitter post that he resigned from this post to engage in political activities aimed at the general election.",
        "Mayanda Dissanayake, who has made a Twitter post citing the news published by an English media that he has left the party, said, \"I will work with confidence in the parliamentary committee of the United People's Shakti.\" \"The news that he has left the party is untrue,\" he said."
      ],
